title: Fairground.2-HI2U
description:
HI2U!

Fairground 2 (c) rondomedia

Release date : 27th of June, 2013
Protection   : Serial
Type         : Simulation
Size         : 32 x 15 mb

Description:
~~~~~~~~~~~~
Enjoy 15 replicas of the most famous portrait and rides round the world in a
realistic simulation. Including booster, Breakdancing, Flyaway, Condor,
ToppleTower and many more.

All rides can be seen in a realistically designed theme park environment at
any time, controlled and experienced.

Features
15 Investments in real true original license r HUSS Park Attractions
Intuitive control
Create your own travel programs and exchange these with your friends
10 driving programs can be recorded and played back at any time per ride
Underlay the driving programs with one of the songs contained about 30
Special effects such as lights, strobes, lasers, scanners, fog, fire and water
provide unique travel programs
Experience the plants in various weather conditions
Different camera views (Onride, offride) provide an up-close experience
Elaborately themed park environment
Park visitors contribute to the atmosphere

Install:
~~~~~~~
Extract & mount the iso and install.
Copy over the cracked content from the /Crack directory on the image to your
Fairground2_DataManaged.
Play the game.
